---

<!-- Stop Learning, Start Absorbing Section -->
<section class='py-16 lg:py-24 space-y-24'>
  <!-- Design: Google x Duolingo Redesign -->
  <div class='max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 md:px-8 flex flex-col gap-10 lg:gap-16'>
    <!-- 1. Hero Headline & Problem/Solution Split -->
    <div class='space-y-12'>
      <div class='text-center space-y-4 max-w-4xl mx-auto'>
        <h2
          class='text-3xl lg:text-5xl font-black tracking-tight leading-tight'
        >
          Berhenti "Belajar Keras". <br />
          <span
            class='text-transparent bg-clip-text bg-linear-to-r from-(--token-purple-base) to-(--token-secondary-gold-base)'
          >
            Mulailah "Menyerap" Aja.
          </span>
        </h2>
        <p class='text-base md:text-xl text-(--token-text-secondary)'>
          Metode tradisional minta kamu jadi robot. Kami minta kamu jadi
          manusia.
