          class='inline-flex items-center px-3 py-1 bg-red-500/10 border border-red-500/20 text-red-400 rounded-lg mx-1 skeuo-inset shadow-[inset_0_2px_4px_oklch(0_0_0/0.6),0_1px_1px_oklch(1_0_0/0.05)]'
        >
          "belajar"</span
        >, <br class='block sm:hidden' /> mulailah
        <span
          class='inline-flex items-center px-3 py-1 bg-(--token-purple-base)/20 border border-purple-500/30 text-purple-300 rounded-lg mx-1 skeuo-inset shadow-[inset_0_2px_4px_oklch(0_0_0/0.6),0_1px_1px_oklch(1_0_0/0.05)]'
