            Otak udah ngebul? Cukup putar audio podcast Jepang sambil rebahan 15
            menit. Nggak usah mikir.
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Card 2: Sibuk -->
        <div class='skeuo-card group p-6 delay-75'>
          <div class='flex items-center gap-4 mb-4'>
            <div
              class='w-12 h-12 rounded-full skeuo-inset border border-orange-500/20 flex items-center justify-center text-orange-400 shrink-0 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform shadow-[inset_0_2px_4px_oklch(0_0_0/0.6),0_1px_1px_oklch(1_0_0/0.05)]'
            >
              <!-- Headphones Icon -->
              <svg
                xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'
                width='24'
                height='24'
                viewBox='0 0 24 24'
                fill='none'
                stroke='currentColor'
                stroke-width='2'
                stroke-linecap='round'
                stroke-linejoin='round'
                class='lucide lucide-headphones'
                ><path d='M3 14v3a2 2 0 0 0 2 2h2a2 2 0 0 0 2-2v-3'></path><path
                  d='M3 14h6'></path><path
                  d='M21 14v3a2 2 0 0 1-2 2h-2a2 2 0 0 1-2-2v-3'></path><path
                  d='M15 14h6'></path><path
                  d='M21 12c0-3.3-2.7-6-6-6h-6c-3.3 0-6 2.7-6 6'></path></svg
              >
            </div>
            <h4 class='text-lg font-bold'>Lagi Sibuk? ğŸƒ</h4>
          </div>
          <p class='text-sm text-gray-400 leading-relaxed'>
            Dengar pas di jalan, di kereta, atau pas lagi masak. Manfaatkan
            "waktu mati" mu tanpa mengganggu jadwal.
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Card 3: Males -->
        <div class='skeuo-card group p-6 delay-150'>
          <div class='flex items-center gap-4 mb-4'>
            <div
              class='w-12 h-12 rounded-full skeuo-inset border border-purple-500/20 flex items-center justify-center text-purple-400 shrink-0 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform shadow-[inset_0_2px_4px_oklch(0_0_0/0.6),0_1px_1px_oklch(1_0_0/0.05)]'
            >
              <!-- TV Icon -->
              <svg
                xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'
                width='24'
                height='24'
                viewBox='0 0 24 24'
                fill='none'
                stroke='currentColor'
                stroke-width='2'
                stroke-linecap='round'
                stroke-linejoin='round'
                class='lucide lucide-tv'
                ><rect width='20' height='15' x='2' y='7' rx='2' ry='2'
                ></rect><polyline points='17 2 12 7 7 2'></polyline></svg
              >
            </div>
            <h4 class='text-lg font-bold'>Lagi Males? ğŸ¦¥</h4>
          </div>
          <p class='text-sm text-gray-400 leading-relaxed'>
            Tonton anime dengan subtitle Jepang aja. Nikmati ceritanya, nggak
            usah dipaksa paham 100%. No pressure.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- 4. Coach's Note -->
    <div
      class='skeuo-card p-6 md:p-8 border-l-4! border-l-(--token-secondary-gold-base)!'
    >
      <div class='flex gap-3 md:gap-5 items-start'>
        <div
          class='shrink-0 text-(--token-secondary-gold-base) mt-1 drop-shadow-[0_0_8px_oklch(0.81_0.15_78/0.4)]'
        >
          <svg
            xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'
            width='32'
            height='32'
            viewBox='0 0 24 24'
            fill='none'
            stroke='currentColor'
            stroke-width='2'
            stroke-linecap='round'
            stroke-linejoin='round'
            class='lucide lucide-info'
            ><circle cx='12' cy='12' r='10'></circle><path d='M12 16v-4'
            ></path><path d='M12 8h.01'></path></svg
          >
        </div>
        <div>
          <h4 class='font-bold text-lg text-white mb-2'>Satu Hal Penting...</h4>
          <p class='text-(--token-text-secondary) leading-relaxed'>
            Kami nggak janji instan. Immersion tetap butuh waktu investasiâ€”kamu
            harus rutin "menyerap" bahasa itu berbulan-bulan. Tapi bedanya,
            prosesnya <span class='text-white font-medium'
              >ringan, menyenangkan, dan nggak bikin burnout</span
            >. Karena otakmu memang diciptakan untuk belajar bahasa dengan cara
            ini sejak lahir.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Feature 1: No Grammar -->
  <div
    class='max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 md:px-8 flex flex-col gap-10 lg:grid lg:grid-cols-12 lg:gap-16 items-start lg:items-stretch'
  >
    <!-- Image (Mobile Order 2, Desktop Left) -->
    <div
      class='order-2 lg:order-0 lg:col-span-5 lg:col-start-1 w-full mx-auto relative'
    >
      <div
        class='sticky top-24 lg:top-32 space-y-6 w-full mx-auto max-w-[420px] lg:max-w-full'
      >
        <div
          class='rounded-2xl overflow-hidden border border-white/10 shadow-2xl skew-y-1 lg:skew-y-2 hover:skew-y-0 transition-transform duration-500 w-full'
        >
          <CldImage
            src='Nggak_Bikin_Kamu_Lancar_Image_76q5so76q5so76q5_k7mexu'
            alt='Ilustrasi: Hafal grammar tidak bikin lancar'
            width={1696}
            height={2528}
            quality='auto'
            format='auto'
            loading='lazy'
            class='block w-full h-auto rounded-2xl bg-[oklch(0.1_0_0)]'
          />
        </div>

        <!-- Moved JLPT text to Left Column -->
        <div
          class='p-4 sm:p-5 rounded-xl bg-red-500/10 border border-red-500/20'
        >
          <div class='flex gap-3 sm:gap-4 items-start'>
            <svg
              xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'
              width='20'
              height='20'
              viewBox='0 0 24 24'
              fill='none'
              stroke='currentColor'
              stroke-width='2'
              stroke-linecap='round'
              stroke-linejoin='round'
              class='lucide lucide-info shrink-0 text-red-500 mt-0.5'
              ><circle cx='12' cy='12' r='10'></circle><path d='M12 16v-4'
              ></path><path d='M12 8h.01'></path></svg
            >
            <p
              class='text-[14px] sm:text-[15px] text-gray-300 leading-relaxed text-pretty'
            >
              <strong class='text-red-400 font-bold'
                >Data dari situs Resmi JLPT "Can-do"</strong
              > sendiri nunjukin: banyak yang lulus N4-N1 tapi masih susah paham percakapan
              kasual atau formal. Bukan karena mereka bodoh, tapi karena <span
                class='text-white font-medium border-b border-red-500/50 pb-0.5'
                >pondasinya salah dari awal</span
              >.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Text Wrapper (Mobile: Hidden/Contents, Desktop: Flex Column) -->
    <div
      class='contents lg:flex lg:col-span-7 lg:flex-col gap-6 lg:justify-center w-full'
    >
      <!-- Header (Mobile Order 1, Desktop Top) -->
      <div class='order-1 flex items-start gap-4'>
        <div
          class='shrink-0 p-3 rounded-xl bg-red-500/10 border border-red-500/20 text-red-400 mt-1'
        >
          <svg
            xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'
            width='24'
            height='24'
            viewBox='0 0 24 24'
            fill='none'
            stroke='currentColor'
            stroke-width='2'
            stroke-linecap='round'
            stroke-linejoin='round'
            class='lucide lucide-x-circle'
            ><circle cx='12' cy='12' r='10'></circle><path d='m15 9-6 6'
            ></path><path d='m9 9 6 6'></path></svg
          >
        </div>
        <div>
          <h3
            class='text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-bold text-white mb-2 leading-tight text-balance'
          >
            Kenapa Hafal Bunpou (Grammar) Nggak Bikin Kamu Lancar?
          </h3>
          <div
            class='h-1 w-20 bg-linear-to-r from-red-500 to-transparent rounded-full'
          >
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Text Body (Mobile Order 3, Desktop Bottom) -->
      <div class='order-3'>
        <div
          class='p-6 sm:p-8 rounded-2xl md:rounded-3xl bg-white/5 border border-white/10 skeuo-inset shadow-[inset_0_2px_4px_oklch(0_0_0/0.6),0_1px_1px_oklch(1_0_0/0.05)] text-[15px] sm:text-base text-(--token-text-secondary) leading-relaxed text-pretty space-y-5'
        >
          <p>
            Hafal bunpou itu kayak hafal rumus fisika: kamu tahu teorinya, bisa
            ngerjain soal di kertas, tapi pas dipraktikkin di dunia nyata,
            otakmu loading lama. Kenapa? Karena bahasa hidup nggak berjalan
            kayak rumus matematika.
          </p>
